{"tid":654170,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭的「母語」好無聊","createTime":"2018-05-05T11:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T05:08:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"968c7117c0ba1ad9632489bffb52a9db96bb461b","tid":654170,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20180505/20381343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F20381343&d=Z0k%2FYHbF8MaaLJQ2u3fBcQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=22e4471a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F20381343&h=0c4dea7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20180505/20381343</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月05日 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭的「母語」好無聊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180505/large/1525428297_b1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F1525428297_b1c0.jpg&h=0793d6a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n這個話題簡單明確又直接了──甚麼是「母語」？一個人出生後，最早接觸、學習、掌握的語言，亦其思維與交往的自然工具，父母的話語就是「母語」。<br />\n<br />\n人不能忘本，一切的「根源」和「基礎」，我們目為「始」，如母校、母國、母法、母財（本錢）、母韻、母音&hellip;&hellip;和母語。人尊重父母，把你帶來這世界，自小教誨，你牙牙學語&hellip;&hellip;至長大成人，也不會將你所得到的，學習和使用的東西拋諸腦後，甚至因為一些骯髒可恥的理由，數典忘祖，不敢回應。<br />\n<br />\n問任何一個香港人：「你的母語是甚麼？」，都可以坦誠回答：「廣東話。」粵語不是方言，也不是地域變體的語言，粵人說粵語，不能政治化官式化以普通話為正規語言教育，忘本是兩頭唔到岸。<br />\n<br />\n香港人向來瞧不起777，除因只是個政治妹仔，表現得吮舐媚主，還欠是非之心法治精神，向賣港奴才傾斜，說她「好打得」已是反諷，林鄭連議員問：「你嘅母語係乜嘢？」時，竟一臉鄙夷望也不敢望：「對唔住，我唔答呢個無聊問題。」<br />\n<br />\n「無聊」？「無膽」而已，一個連父母、祖宗都無膽面對和承認的奴才，還可指望她維護港人文化、福祉、本土風俗、核心價值嗎？有奶便是娘，只愛飼以假母乳的富貴後底乸，忘記生母了。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"5c7ddaee66d9765d5d382be43f48f86ae4aeb47a","tid":654170,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:38:31.000Z","msg":"怕?"},{"pid":"6e504a3bd906ae8b33c51b48fe23a6d4139edeee","tid":654170,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:51:57.000Z","msg":"立法會唔好講咁多政治"},{"pid":"0bd06f9fa67d36834dcab964072bd4ca689f8453","tid":654170,"uid":19072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35352e65ab7ff0889675cebf9d580cb1e5989dc5","tid":654170,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T01:21:08.000Z","msg":"呢篇嘢已經伸延到種族鬥爭了"},{"pid":"aee645d3dcf4922c0de06b77b37d0bc6ccc32837","tid":654170,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:26:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"474d7f1fca64dc2871e427626623fac86655b561","tid":654170,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:48:07.000Z","msg":"繼689唔答東亞運支持港隊之後<br />\n<br />\n又一個777唔答香港自己母語廣東話的官<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58f68b30e5988d27c7d6e54b3611432af74061c","tid":654170,"uid":22535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:03:50.000Z","msg":"佢波都無，真係無乳嫁。你問佢，佢點答你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d49b855507f24327e75186446592f628d86df2","tid":654170,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35352e65ab7ff0889675cebf9d580cb1e5989dc5","tid":654170,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T01:21:08.000Z","msg":"呢篇嘢已經伸延到種族鬥爭了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:08:48.000Z","msg":"中共一早就發動緊種族戰爭<br />\n由佢地決定想消滅粵語果一刻香港同中國已經唔可以共存"}]}